---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Daoist Philosophy" description="Explore Daoist philosophy - the Tao Te Ching, Zhuangzi's wisdom, and the practical application of Daoism in modern life.">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-600 via-cyan-600 to-teal-700 text-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <span class="text-teal-200 text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase">Philosophy</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mt-2 mb-4">Daoist Philosophy</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-teal-100">The way of nature, the art of letting go. China's native philosophy offers timeless wisdom for modern life.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <a href="/daoism/taoteching" class="group bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">📖</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-teal-600 transition-colors">Tao Te Ching</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600">Laozi's 5,000-character masterpiece—the foundational text of Daoism and one of the world's great spiritual works.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/daoism/zhuangzi" class="group bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🦋</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-teal-600 transition-colors">Zhuangzi</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600">The playful philosopher whose parables and stories challenge everything we think we know.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/daoism/yinyang" class="group bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">☯️</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-teal-600 transition-colors">Yin & Yang</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600">The cosmic dance of opposites—how apparent contradictions create harmony in nature.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/daoism/modern" class="group bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🌿</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-teal-600 transition-colors">Daoism Today</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600">Applying ancient wisdom to modern challenges—stress, creativity, leadership, and well-being.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-8">Featured Articles</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <article class="group">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-400 to-cyan-600 rounded-xl mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-5xl">🌀</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2">Tao Te Ching: Chapter 1 Explained</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">The most famous opening lines in Eastern philosophy decoded.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="group">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-400 to-blue-600 rounded-xl mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-5xl">🦋</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2">The Butterfly Dream: Zhuangzi's Famous Parable</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">Was Zhuangzi a butterfly dreaming he was a man, or a man dreaming he was a butterfly?</p>
        </article>
        <article class="group">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-400 to-teal-600 rounded-xl mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-5xl">🌊</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2">Wu Wei: The Art of Non-Action</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">The Daoist concept that sounds passive but is actually the ultimate effectiveness.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
